00028 #define INITIAL_MASK 0xf

00030 static size_t fast_ptr_hash(dfsch_object_t* ptr){
00031   size_t p = (size_t) ptr;
00032 
00033   p ^= (p >> 3) | (p << (CHAR_BIT*sizeof(size_t) - 3));
00034   p ^= (p << 12) | (p >> (CHAR_BIT*sizeof(size_t) - 12));
00035 
00036   return p;
00037 }

00039 static dfsch_eqhash_entry_t** alloc_vector(size_t mask){
00040   return GC_MALLOC(sizeof(dfsch_eqhash_entry_t*) * (mask + 1));
00041 }

00043 void dfsch_eqhash_init(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash, int start_large){
00044   int i;
00045   if (start_large){
00046     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE * 2; i++){
00047       hash->contents.large.cache[i] = NULL;
00048     }
00049     hash->contents.large.mask = INITIAL_MASK;
00050     hash->contents.large.count = 0;
00051     hash->contents.large.vector = alloc_vector(INITIAL_MASK);
00052   } else {
00053     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00054       hash->contents.small.keys[i] = DFSCH_INVALID_OBJECT;
00055       hash->contents.small.values[i] = NULL;
00056       hash->contents.small.flags[i] = 0;
00057     }
00058   }
00059   hash->is_large = start_large;
00060 }

00074 #define BUCKET(hash, index)                     \
00075   (hash->contents.large.vector[(index) & hash->contents.large.mask])

00077 static void convert_to_large(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash){
00078   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t** vector = alloc_vector(INITIAL_MASK);
00079   size_t h;
00080   int i;
00081   
00082   for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00083     if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] != DFSCH_INVALID_OBJECT){
00084       h = fast_ptr_hash(hash->contents.small.keys[i]);
00085       vector[h & INITIAL_MASK] = alloc_entry(hash->contents.small.keys[i],
00086                                              hash->contents.small.values[i],
00087                                              hash->contents.small.flags[i],
00088                                              vector[h & INITIAL_MASK]);
00089     }
00090   }
00091 
00092   for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE * 2; i++){
00093     hash->contents.large.cache[i] = NULL;
00094   }
00095   
00096   hash->contents.large.vector = vector;
00097   hash->contents.large.count = DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE;
00098   hash->contents.large.mask = INITIAL_MASK;  
00099   hash->is_large = 1;
00100 }

00102 static void grow_hash(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash){
00103   size_t new_mask = ((hash->contents.large.mask + 1) * 2) - 1;
00104   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t** vector = alloc_vector(new_mask);
00105   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* i;
00106   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* j;
00107   int k;
00108   size_t h;
00109 
00110   for (k = 0; k <= hash->contents.large.mask; k++){
00111     i = hash->contents.large.vector[k];
00112     while (i){
00113       j = i->next;
00114       h = fast_ptr_hash(i->key);
00115       i->next = vector[h & new_mask];
00116       vector[h & new_mask] = i;
00117       i = j;
00118     }
00119   }
00120 
00121   hash->contents.large.vector = vector;
00122   hash->contents.large.mask = new_mask;
00123 }

00125 void dfsch_eqhash_put(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash,
00126                       dfsch_object_t* key, dfsch_object_t* value){
00127   if (DFSCH_LIKELY(!hash->is_large)){
00128     int i;
00129     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00130       if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] == DFSCH_INVALID_OBJECT){
00131         hash->contents.small.keys[i] = key;
00132         hash->contents.small.values[i] = value;
00133         return;
00134       }
00135     }
00136 
00137     convert_to_large(hash);
00138   }
00139   size_t h = fast_ptr_hash(key);
00140   hash->contents.large.count++;
00141   if (DFSCH_UNLIKELY(hash->contents.large.count / 2 
00142                      > hash->contents.large.mask)){
00143     grow_hash(hash);
00144   }
00145   BUCKET(hash, h) = alloc_entry(key, value, 0, BUCKET(hash,h));
00146 }

00148 static dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* find_entry(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash, 
00149                                         dfsch_object_t* key){
00150   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* i;
00151   size_t h;
00152   h = fast_ptr_hash(key);
00153   DFSCH_PREFETCH(BUCKET(hash, h));
00154   i = hash->contents.large.cache[(h >> 10) % DFSCH_EQHASH_CACHE_SIZE];
00155   if (DFSCH_LIKELY(i) && 
00156       DFSCH_UNLIKELY(i->key == key)){
00157     return i;
00158   }
00159   
00160   i = BUCKET(hash, h);
00161   while (i){
00162     if (DFSCH_LIKELY(i->key == key)){
00163       hash->contents.large.cache[(h >> 10) % DFSCH_EQHASH_CACHE_SIZE] = i;
00164       return i;
00165     }
00166     i = i->next;
00167   }
00168   return NULL;
00169 }

00171 static int delete_entry(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash, 
00172                         dfsch_object_t* key){
00173   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* i;
00174   dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* j;  
00175   size_t h;
00176   h = fast_ptr_hash(key);
00177   
00178   i = BUCKET(hash, h);
00179   while (i){
00180     if (i->key == key){
00181       if (hash->contents.large.cache[(h >> 10) % DFSCH_EQHASH_CACHE_SIZE] == i){
00182         hash->contents.large.cache[(h >> 10) % DFSCH_EQHASH_CACHE_SIZE] = NULL;
00183       }
00184       if (j) {
00185         j->next = i->next;
00186       } else {
00187         BUCKET(hash, h) = i->next;
00188       }
00189       return 1;
00190     }
00191     j = i;
00192     i = i->next;
00193   }
00194   return 0;
00195 }

00197 void dfsch_eqhash_set(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash,
00198                       dfsch_object_t* key, dfsch_object_t* value){
00199   if (hash->is_large){
00200     dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* e = find_entry(hash, key);
00201     if (e) {
00202       e->value = value;
00203       return;
00204     }
00205   } else {
00206     int i;
00207     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00208       if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] == key){
00209         hash->contents.small.values[i] = value;
00210         return;
00211       }
00212     }
00213   }
00214   dfsch_eqhash_put(hash, key, value);  
00215 }

00269 dfsch_object_t* dfsch_eqhash_ref(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash,
00270                                  dfsch_object_t* key){
00271   if (DFSCH_UNLIKELY(hash->is_large)){
00272     dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* e = find_entry(hash, key);
00273     if (e) {
00274       return e->value;
00275     }
00276   } else {
00277     int i;
00278     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00279       if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] == key){
00280         return hash->contents.small.values[i];
00281       }
00282     }
00283   }  
00284   return DFSCH_INVALID_OBJECT;  
00285 }
00286 int dfsch_eqhash_ref_ex(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash,
00287                         dfsch_object_t* key, 
00288                         dfsch_object_t** value, short *flags,
00289                         dfsch_eqhash_entry_t** entry){
00290   if (hash->is_large){
00291     dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* e = find_entry(hash, key);
00292     if (e) {
00293       if (value){
00294         *value = e->value;
00295       }
00296       if (flags){
00297         *flags = e->flags;
00298       }
00299       if (entry){
00300         *entry = e;
00301       }
00302       return 1;
00303     }
00304   } else {
00305     int i;
00306     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00307       if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] == key){
00308         if (value) {
00309           *value = hash->contents.small.values[i];
00310         }
00311         if (flags) {
00312           *flags = hash->contents.small.flags[i];
00313         }
00314         return 1;
00315       }
00316     }
00317   }  
00318   return 0;  
00319 }
00320 dfsch_object_t* dfsch_eqhash_2_alist(dfsch_eqhash_t* hash){
00321   dfsch_object_t* result = NULL;
00322   int i;
00323 
00324   if (hash->is_large){
00325     for (i = 0; i <= hash->contents.large.mask; i++){
00326       dfsch_eqhash_entry_t* e = hash->contents.large.vector[i];
00327       while (e){
00328         result = dfsch_cons(dfsch_list(2, e->key, e->value), result);
00329         e = e->next;
00330       }
00331     }
00332   } else {
00333     for (i = 0; i < DFSCH_EQHASH_SMALL_SIZE; i++){
00334       if (hash->contents.small.keys[i] != DFSCH_INVALID_OBJECT){
00335         result = dfsch_cons(dfsch_list(2,
00336                                        hash->contents.small.keys[i],
00337                                        hash->contents.small.values[i]),
00338                             result);
00339       }
00340     }
00341   }
00342   return result;
00343 }
